CBRE & Leedwell Property are excited to present, 222 Fairbairn Road, Sunshine West, for lease.

Centrally located on Sunshine West’s major thoroughfare, 222 Fairbairn Road offers fantastic exposure to passing traffic, along with easy access to the freeway network. The Melbourne CBD and Footscray are accessed via Somerville Road and the freeway network can be accessed via two routes: Boundary Road Sunshine West entry/exit ramp, or the Grieve Parade Altona entry/exit.

While exposure to passing car and truck traffic is the major draw-card to this development, the site is accessed via a large service road ensuring truck and container access is stress free.  

Key Highlights Include:
+   Sunshine West's latest business address READY TO MOVE IN
+   Large brand new Showroom/Warehouse
+   Corner position available with abundance of natural light
+   Maximum signage and brand awareness
+   Mezzanine office: 100sqm*
+   Commercial display area
+   High clearance rear-loading warehouse
+   Modern glass and alucobond façade
+   Surplus on site car parking
+   5m x 5m wide motorised roller shutter door
+   Large concrete rear loading areas
+   Easy access via Service Road for both trucks and customer vehicles
+   Staff amenities
+   Modern landscaping
+   Areas range from: 588sqm* - 1,176sqm*

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the listed agents.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present 90-94 Proximity Drive, Sunshine West, for lease.

Located in the highly accessible Proximity Estate, this opportunity is one of only a few that can be found east of the Western Ring Road.

At 90-94 Proximity Drive, Sunshine West, occupiers will be provided with direct access to Melbourne's arterial road network via Fairbairn and Little Boundary Roads, with on-flows to the Melbourne CBD, Port and Tullamarine Airport.

Two properties are available, each with 637sqm* of total building area.

Key property features include:
+ Access between warehouses and yard available
+ High clearance warehouse
+ Motorised roller shutter door
+ Individually titled tenancy
+ Exclusive secure gate access and yard
+ Modern open plan offices and staff amenities
+ Three phase power
+ Off street parking

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team.
